# Voice Profile — [ Your Name ]

> Source of truth for HOW YOU write and think — unique to you, never shared. `/onboard` (the Taste
> Interview) fills this. Read alongside `references/about-me.md` (the deeper master profile),
> `.claude/rules/voice.md` (outreach), and `.claude/rules/anti-ai.md`. Replace every `[ xxx ]`.
> The job: close the gap between how you actually TALK and how AI tools make you WRITE. Inhabit your
> voice, don't imitate a generic one.
>
> **REFER, DO NOT ASSUME.** Skills draw only from what is recorded here and in about-me.md. If a
> story, example, number, or detail isn't captured, they ask or leave it out — never invent or infer
> to fill a gap. Missing material gets flagged (e.g. `[needs: …]`), never guessed.

